data.title: Barbara Higbie & Teresa Trull visit The Hear and Now - July 30, 2015
data.meta_description: In anticipation of their Saturday, August 1, concert at the Freight & Salvage Coffeehouse, longtime musical partners Barbara Higbie and Teresa Trull shared music they’ve recorded together and separately, and chatted with host Derk Richardson. After that, a lot of classic West Coast folk-rock and some wild-card jazz and experimental musical selections.
